已知信息：
'A substance that has been shown by an extensive set of analytical tests to be authentic material that should be of high purity. This standard can be:—obtained from an officially recognized source;
—prepared by independent synthesis;
—obtained from existing production material of high purity; or
—prepared by further purification of existing production material.'可被翻译为：经大量分析试验证明为真实材料的物质，应具有高纯度。该标准可以是:-从官方认可的来源获得;
-独立合成制备;
-从现有的高纯度生产材料中获得;或
-通过进一步提纯现有生产材料制备。
'A substance that has been shown by an extensive set of analytical tests to be authentic material that should be of high purity. This standard can be: (1) obtained from an officially recognised source, or (2) prepared by independent synthesis, or (3) obtained from existing production material of high purity, or (4) prepared by further purification of existing production material.'可被翻译为：通过一系列分析试验表明其真实性的高纯度物质。可由以下方式得到: (1)来自于认可的官方(2)单独合成(3)来自于现有的高纯度的生产产品(4)对现有生产产品进行进一步纯化。
'A substance other than a starting material, intermediate, or solvent that is used in the manufacture of a new drug substance.'可被翻译为：一种与起始物、中间体或溶剂不同的物质，在新原料药的生产中使用。
'A reference substance used as a physical or chemical reference for drug identification, inspection, and content determination.'可被翻译为：用于物理或化学方法进行药品鉴别、检查、含量测定对照的标准物质。

根据上述已知信息，请将'A high-purity non-standard substance provided by a pharmaceutical reference substance development institution.'翻译为中文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'A compound having a chemical structure similar to that of existing drug molecules.'可被翻译为：与现有药物分子在化学结构上具有相似性的化合物。
'A compound with the same molecular formula as the drug substance that differs in the spatial arrangement of atoms within the molecule and is a non-superimposable mirror image.'可被翻译为：与药物具有相同的分子式，但其分子中原子的空间排列不同并且为不能重合的镜像的化合物。
'Similarity of compounds to known drugs. A concept that is similar to a drug and affects the success of drug development, including the pharmaceutical properties of the lead compound, pharmacokinetic parameters, and drug safety.'可被翻译为：化合物与已知药物的相似性。表示某些类似于药物性质又影响药物开发成功与否的概念，内容包含先导化合物的药学性质、药动学参数和药物安全性等。
'1.A substance, other than the active pharmaceutical ingredient, which has been appropriately evaluated for safety and is included in a drug delivery system to:—aid in the processing of the drug delivery system during its manufacture;
—protect, support or enhance stability, bioavailability or patient acceptability;
—assist in pharmaceutical product identification; or
—enhance any other attribute of the overall safety and effectiveness of the drug during its storage or use.
2.A substance, other than the active pharmaceutical ingredient (API), which has been appropriately evaluated for safety and is included in a medicines delivery system to:—aid in the processing of the medicines delivery system during its manufacture;
—protect, support or enhance stability, bioavailability or patient acceptability;
—assist in pharmaceutical product identification; or
—enhance any other attribute of the overall safety and effectiveness of the medicine during its storage or use.'可被翻译为：1.一种非活性药物成分的物质，已经过适当的安全性评估，并包含在给药系统中，以在给药系统生产过程中辅助处理;
-保护、支持或增强稳定性、生物利用度或患者可接受性;
-协助药品鉴定;或
-在储存或使用期间增强药物整体安全性和有效性的任何其他属性。
2.一种非活性药物成分(API)的物质，已经过适当的安全性评估，并包含在药物输送系统中，以在药物输送系统生产过程中辅助处理;
-保护、支持或增强稳定性、生物利用度或患者可接受性;
-协助药品鉴定;或
-在储存或使用期间增强药物整体安全性和有效性的任何其他属性。

根据上述已知信息，请将'A compound having a structural characteristic necessary for the action of a drug. The compound is not metabolized or transformed in living organisms, avoiding the production of certain toxic metabolites.'翻译为中文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。
